<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="summer-release-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1>2026 Summer Release</h1>
      <p class="lead">New features and improvements to make hosting and traveling even better</p>
      <p>Discover what's new this summer and how these updates can help you get more out of Wanderlust.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>Simplifying service fees</h2>
        <p>We're making changes to our fee structure to make pricing more transparent for both hosts and guests.</p>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>What's changing</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Clearer fee breakdowns at checkout</li>
            <li>More predictable pricing for guests</li>
            <li>Better understanding of host earnings</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Get details →</a>

        <h2>Reservations, redesigned</h2>
        <p>Our new reservation system makes managing bookings easier than ever before.</p>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>New features</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Streamlined booking flow</li>
            <li>Improved calendar management</li>
            <li>Better guest communication tools</li>
            <li>Enhanced booking confirmation process</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read more →</a>

        <h2>The right price for every season</h2>
        <p>Smart pricing tools help you set competitive rates year-round.</p>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Enhanced pricing tools</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Seasonal pricing recommendations</li>
            <li>Local demand insights</li>
            <li>Automated price adjustments</li>
            <li>Competitor analysis</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read more →</a>

        <h2>A more insightful Calendar</h2>
        <p>Visualize your bookings, pricing, and availability in one place.</p>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Calendar improvements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Better booking visualization</li>
            <li>Integrated pricing display</li>
            <li>Enhanced availability management</li>
            <li>Sync with external calendars</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read more →</a>

        <h2>Auto-reply for common questions</h2>
        <p>Save time with automated responses to frequently asked questions.</p>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Messaging upgrades</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Pre-built response templates</li>
            <li>Smart suggestions based on context</li>
            <li>Multi-language support</li>
            <li>Customizable auto-replies</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Read more →</a>

        <h2>Enhanced guest reviews</h2>
        <p>New review features help you build your reputation and attract more bookings.</p>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Review improvements</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Detailed review categories</li>
            <li>Better review response tools</li>
            <li>Review trend analysis</li>
            <li>Guest feedback highlights</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">Learn more →</a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick links</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="/hosting-resources">Hosting resources</a></li>
            <li><a href="/community-forum">Community forum</a></li>
            <li><a href="/helpcenter">Help Center</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Need help?</h3>
          <p>Our support team can help you with any questions about the new features.</p>
          <a href="/helpcenter" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Contact Support</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Share feedback</h3>
          <p>Let us know what you think about the new features.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Send feedback</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
